    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
            <p>Never published before <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>117900</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    
                    <lb n="1"/><date calendar="egyptian"><expan><abbr><am><g type="year">𐅹</g></am></abbr> <ex>ἔτους</ex></expan> 
                    <num type="cardinal" value="4"><g type="alphabetic">δ</g></num></date> 
                    <persName type="attested" key=""><name nymRef="#Ζην_"><seg part="I">Ζην</seg><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></name>
                    <lb n="2"/><persName type="attested" key=""><name nymRef="#Ἁνίοχος" type="patronymic">Ἁνιόχο<unclear>υ</unclear></name></persName></persName>
	 </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p/>
 </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p>An 4. Zèn<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> fils d'Haniokhos.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p>Year 4. Zen<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> son of Haniochos.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
            <p>Anno 4. Zen<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> figlio di Haniochos.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="ar">
            <p>السنة 4. زين [---] بن هانيوخوس.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
	<p>J.M. Reynolds observed that the stonecutter perhaps did not finish the name beginning with <foreign xml:lang="grc">Ζην</foreign>- because avoiding an isolated delta
	    already cut there.</p>
            <p>Most names dated with a year are considered of Roman time. However J.M. Reynolds thought that the lettering of this one was older. If so, we do not know to 
            which event the era was related.</p>            
            </div></body>
    </text>
